Single Line Macro

Syntax: MACRO macroname const-value
Example:	MACRO MAX 100

Call:
Example: mov eax,MAX


Conditional Macros

1.	if-endif/if-else-endif:
There are 6 logical conditions checked by ‘if’:
‘==’:	EQ
‘!=’:	NE
‘>=’:	GE
‘<=’:	LE
‘<’:	LT
‘>’:	GT

Syntax:
i.	if ( condition )
		....
		...
	endif
ii.	if ( condition )
		...
		...
	else
		...
		...
	endif
  
 2.while-endwhile   (under development)
  
